---
// DNA Mutants - University Project
---

<section class="card p-6 sm:p-8 relative overflow-hidden" style="border-color: var(--comic-yellow);">
  <!-- Comic Badge -->
  <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 comic-badge" style="background: var(--comic-yellow); color: var(--comic-black); font-size: 0.7rem;">
    University
  </div>

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
         style="background: var(--comic-yellow); border: 3px solid var(--comic-black); box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--comic-black);">
      <i class="fas fa-dna text-white text-2xl"></i>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="comic-title text-2xl" style="color: var(--comic-yellow-dark);">DNA Mutants</h3>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); color: var(--gray-600); font-weight: 700;">Genetic Analysis Tool</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Description -->
  <div class="speech-bubble mb-4">
    <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); color: var(--comic-black); font-weight: 700;">
      A university project focused on DNA sequence analysis to detect mutant patterns in genetic data using algorithms and matrix evaluation.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p class="text-sm" style="font-family: var(--font-body); color: var(--gray-600); font-weight: 700;">
    This was one of my earliest projects, built as part of my academic coursework exploring computational biology concepts.
  </p>
</section>